title: Woman struck by sheriff's vehicle at Stephon Clark vigil
text:
Woman struck by sheriff's vehicle at Stephon Clark vigil 3:11pm EDT - 01:49 
Tensions mounted over the fatal police shooting of an unarmed black man in Sacramento, California, where a protester sustained minor injuries when struck by a sheriff’s patrol car that was under attack by demonstrators, authorities said on Sunday.
